Package gbssg.Jamalia_Polat_Vrlec

Interface ISerializer

All Known Implementing Classes:
Point2D, Point3D, Polyeder, Polygon, Vector2D, Vector3D
public interface ISerializer
This interface is implemented in classes of objects which have to be projected in some way or another. Classes which implement this interface are Vector2d, Vector3D, Point2D, Point3, Polygon and Polyeder.
Version:
1.0
Author:
